            "dialogs": [
                {
                    "id" : "caught-1" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Knight",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Here's our traitor. You won't get away as easily this time."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "peasant1",
            "dialogs": [
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-1" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Are you the tr...",
                    "nextId": "peasant1-2"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-2" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Do you really need to ask?",
                    "nextId": "peasant1-3"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-3" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Well, I'm just glad someone is helping out the rebels.",
                    "nextId": "peasant1-4"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-4" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "The king is skinning us alive! Only last year, they took my son...",
                    "nextId": "peasant1-5"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant1-5" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "But you must go, you must leave the city before dawn."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "peasant2",
            "dialogs": [
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-1" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "Traitor! Why the hell do you want to help those filthy rebels?",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-2"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-2" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "The king cares only about his well being.",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-3"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-3" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "He'd sell your soul to the devil if that could bring him some benefit.",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-4"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-4" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "He even uses the sons of his people as slaves in the northern mines! Look, I can prove it!",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-5"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-5" ,
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Peasant",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "This is horrifying. My nephew went to the north, they said he had the prospect of a better life.",
                    "nextId": "peasant2-6"
                },
                {
                    "id" : "peasant2-6",
                    "character" : {
                        "name": "Prisoner",
                        "mood": "serious"
                    },
                    "text": "I'm sorry..."
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
